route-policy.rpl-route-policy:
route-policy s0_out
  set extcommunity rt high_bw additive
  pass
end-policy

route-policy multipath
  set path-selection multipath advertise
end-policy

route-policy pass_with_SID_extcomm
  if destination in node_SID then
    set extcommunity rt node_SID
  endif
  if destination in anycast_SID then
    set extcommunity rt anycast_SID
  endif
  pass
end-policy

cli.commitMessageFormat:
System message at $(time)...
Commit performed by $(user) via $(proto) using $(ctx).
cli.forcedExitFormat: \nYou are forced out of configure mode by $(sender).\n
